VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Grok, or whether you\'re using a local version of AI, you can select your models. So, we\'ll look at the settings here just briefly, and then we\'ll do a quick demo.'

[00:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'So, you\'ve got your models that you can download. This particular list today has 67 potential models. Now, you can see I\'ve got a lot of uh memory, 256 GB.'

